    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I have tracked this down to https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/blob/1abfaa94af3b3972cf0c081dc8a8626ce6bcf052/OpenRA.Mods.Common/Activities/Enter.cs#L257-L259\r\nwhere `savedPos` was saved in the tick before the actors were loaded into the APC.\r\n\r\n\r\nI don't yet understand why \"always call done for movable targets and use a separate exit activity\" didn't apply in this specific case and not the vast majority where we have never seen this bug before."
